{"tid":599243,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[圍爐]「就算你後悔都唔好同我講」","createTime":"2018-03-20T08:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T13:31:56.000Z","uid":159659,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ca674d2fedf8faa71f85a37d2469bb2c02ec2b98","tid":599243,"uid":159659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125b6dde62e7763f5e832bbd9ee9f5c23b0db52d","tid":599243,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"錯了嗎 後悔了嗎"},{"pid":"bad9063a7e80bbbea78d28e1bd0033d1377680a6","tid":599243,"uid":159659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"唔係初戀<br />\n但係咁多個之中愛得最深就係佢<br />\nd人話男人嘅愛同女人嘅處一樣 只可以俾一個人<br />\n我真係明點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔會敢咁義無反顧去愛一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f41b7e2681300ee26664b3c1d09b2718bb434f","tid":599243,"uid":7915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:42:42.000Z","msg":"人地根本冇後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855d36327b5bc69a89700887294472e76008b3e6","tid":599243,"uid":167068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"太愛一個人最後傷嘅只係自己<br />\n你會因爲咁而冇咗原本嘅自己<br />\n佢會覺得你變咗 而選擇離開你<br />\n所以愛一個人 <br />\n唔一定要比哂你最好嘅野佢<br />\n做番自己就夠了"},{"pid":"e1409ca2daaf49eccc9ff78a78529713fdf30356","tid":599243,"uid":46609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"感情冇得話付出就有收穫<br />\n正如有人好鐘意你，為左你可以花好多心思唔等於你就會鐘意佢一樣"},{"pid":"1b3e90c1240ecc1e29f659d0071fdd278b866927","tid":599243,"uid":146893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-2